comments:
That part which until 1.4.1934 formed part of the parish of Wirksworth. 
    See also Table 2, note (i).

Abolished 1.4.1968 and added to the parish of Derby. See 
    also Table 2, notes (f) and (n).

That part which until 1.4.1934 formed parts of the parishes of Mackworth and Markeaton. 
    See also Table 2, note (e).

Created 1.10.1897 out of the parishes of Dethick & Lea and Crich. 
    See also Table 2, note (p).
Abolished 1.10.1897 and added to the parish of Dethick, Lea & Holloway.
Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the parish of Belper.

Abolished 24.3.1889 and divided between the parishes of Idridgehay 
    & Alton and Kirk Ireton. See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Allestree, 
    Derby, Darley Abbey and Mackworth. See also Table 2, notes (c), (d) and 
    (e).

Created 1.10.1897 out of the parish of Duffield. Abolished 1.4.1974 
    and added to the parish of Belper.

Abolished 25.3.1886 and divided between the parishes of Weston 
    Underwood and Hulland Ward. See also Table 2, note (a).
